{"tid":1796021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭發表聖誕祝賀　32 秒片段林鄭僅現身 11 秒　發言只有 37 字","createTime":"2019-12-24T10:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T08:25:04.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":182,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"589f6d32480e8cef7167bcf7ce683b51615a96a3","tid":1796021,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screenshot202019-12-2420at206.13.5120PM20120copy_guCMP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreenshot202019-12-2420at206.13.5120PM20120copy_guCMP_1200x0.png&h=b99c1bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日是平安夜，行政長官林鄭月娥傍晚 6 時在社交網站發聖誕祝福短片。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，短片全長只有 32 秒，當中大部份時間都是影著維港夜景、摩天輪和聖誕樹燈燈飾，林鄭月娥在短片中僅現身 11 秒，發言全文僅 37 個字，「聖誕係一個普天同慶嘅日子，我喺呢度，祝願全港市民，今年有一個平和安穩愉快嘅聖誕節。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=805320349881549&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D805320349881549%26_rdr&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=d5ddbfe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=805320349881549&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"2ca9c02168128090df9d0fe29f40d2f608f53480","tid":1796021,"uid":36157,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"偽政府倒台"},{"pid":"bb39fdafaac8c17735919368dd74efabfc3197a5","tid":1796021,"uid":49392,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"我唔屌你個含撚笨柒個老母嘅生滋甩毛爛臭化花柳白濁梅毒性冷感閪都唔撚柒得嘅"},{"pid":"55e435c212b8902aaac9943d047e749a4527e59f","tid":1796021,"uid":58164,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"鬼影<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9a1f92a4ccee841ee9ca85c4a9a1358fcab73a","tid":1796021,"uid":73915,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T1